'''''Leukemia & Lymphoma''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[public health journal|medical journal]] published by [[Taylor & Francis|Taylor and Francis]]. It includes full-length papers and reviews on basic and clinical aspects of hematologic malignancies.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://informahealthcare.com/page/Description?journalCode=lal#AimsAndScope |title= Leukemia & Lymphoma - Aims and Scope|accessdate=2010-01-15 |format= |work=}}</ref> The [[Editor-in-chief|editors-in-chief]] of ''Leukemia & Lymphoma'' are Aaron Polliack, Koen Van Besien, and John Saymour.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://informahealthcare.com/page/EditorialAdvisoryBoard?journalCode=lal|title=Leukemia & Lymphoma - Editorial Board Members|accessdate=2010-01-15 |format= |work=}}</ref>

==Indexing==
The journal is abstracted and indexed in the [[Web of Science]], [[PubMed]], [[Chemical Abstracts Service|Chemical Abstracts]], and others. According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', the journal has a 2009 [[impact factor]] of 2.397.<ref name=WoS>{{cite web |url=http://isiwebofknowledge.com |title=Web of Science |year=2011 |accessdate=2011-05-27}}</ref>

